---

### **Short Interview Summary**

> Laravel handles environment configurations using **.env files** and the `env()` helper.
> These variables are loaded into **config files**, which the **Service Container** injects throughout the app.
> This approach keeps settings **secure, environment-specific, and flexible**.

---



